item.description:
@I_pker_I wrote:

this is a got tut for ya

1: go to my computer
2: click on local disk C:
3: click on program files
4: click on watever you saved moparscape as
5: click on all ID’s
6: then click on items
7: thats a list of all of the items

to spawn one this is wat u type: ::pickup (item code number) (how many you want)

for example: ::pickup 1042 999999999

that willl give u 999m blue p hats[br][size=1]Posted at: November 26, 2006, 10:20:35 AM[/size][hr]but here r a few items that will lock up ur account if u spawn them

1: fire cape
2: fury amulet
3: anything from the mage training arena (inifnity, master wand…etc…)
4: jester hats, bobble hats, jester scarfes …etc…
5: mainly everything that has obsidian routes
6: black robes (but who wants those)
